Package com.kuka.connectivity.fri

This package realizes the KUKA Fast Robot Interface.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IFRISessionListener A FRI-Session listener may be set for using the Fast Robot Interface.
 

Class Summary
FRIChannelInformation Immutable object, which provides information of the FRI Channel.
FRIConfiguration Provides configuration information about the KUKA FRI channel.
FRIJointOverlay Class for overlaying joint specific motions by using the Fast Robot Interface (FRI).
FRIMotionOverlayMapper Mapper for FRI motion overlays.
FRISession Class to open the FRI channel from the KUKA controller to a remote system.
 

Enum Summary
ClientCommandMode Defines the types of the FRI client commands.
FRIChannelInformation.FRIConnectionQuality Defines the types of the FRI connection quality.
FRIChannelInformation.FRISessionState Enumeration of the FRI session state.
 

Package com.kuka.connectivity.fri Description

This package realizes the KUKA Fast Robot Interface.
